Item.value: Asses this Catalog & Standard Part Request. If there is information missing for further processing please get in contact with the requestor to ask for additional information. Then decide on creating a new Catalog Part (Create Catalog Part) or to reject the request (Reject Request). With your decision you automatically claim this request for further processing.

The requestor provided CATParts and/or CATDrawings with the CSP Request Form. Please check the quality of the provided Datasets by reviewing them in CAD. Then decide on keeping or removing them from the generated Catalog Part or Catalog Definition Article.

Complete following tasks to refine the target Catalog Part: - Check all properties - Check data sheets - Check for provided 3D data and create the corresponding 3D data for CAD - Add classification - Add material and check for hazardous material
Complete this task by selecting the release status according to the proposed target release status or reject the request.
